🌸 Mission Statement

Between Pauses AI exists to create understanding around stuttering, communication differences, and neuroscience through accessible education, empathy, and technology.

The project aims to combine:
-🧠 science
-💻 accessibility
-💛 emotional support
-🎤 communication awareness

to make speech-related conversations more inclusive and compassionate.

Rather than focusing on “fixing” speech differences, Between Pauses AI focuses on:
-awareness
-inclusion
-understanding
-accessible learning
-emotionally safe communication spaces

The initiative believes every person deserves patience, understanding, and the freedom to communicate without shame.
